channel.title: Help people cant connect to my server
channel.description: I made my server and Downloaded everything i needed i made the NO-IP account i named it shockscape.no-ip.org And when i try to register it to the forums is says my server needs to be online to register it.And when i am online on my server when im doing this.Any 1 please help.

item.title: Help people cant connect to my server
item.dc:creator: @p00n99range p00n99range
item.description:
@p00n99range wrote:

[quote=“Elite Jamie, post:2, topic:11901”]well for starters it might be your router settings/portforward or your firewall

you may wanna consider useing utorrent?

http://www.google.com/forums/showthread.php?t=16608&highlight=utorrent[/quote]

Utorrent doesn’t always work with portforwarding. I suggest going to portforwarding.com or going from your router provider. (comcast etc…) you would type like 192.168.0.1 into your link and a thing would pop up. just a example.
